    • Plant

      public Plant​(java.lang.String scientificName, java.lang.String commonName, java.lang.String plantType, int lepsSupported, int cost, java.lang.String weatherType, java.lang.String moistureType, java.lang.String soilType)
      Constructor for Plant. Assigns all attributes of plant an appropriate value.
      Parameters:
      scientificName - the scientific name of the plant
      commonName - the common name of the plant
      plantType - if the plant type is either woody or herbaceous
      lepsSupported - the number of leps the plant supports
      cost - the cost of the plant
      weatherType - the amount of sun exposure of the plant
      moistureType - the moisture level of the soil the plant is grown in
      soilType - the soil type the plant is grown in
